Features
========

    * Ask the user if he wants to save the current note when it is closed
      if the contents have diverged from the ones of the backing file.

    * Warn about unsaved notes on application close.

    * Editable key bindings.

    * Editable color scheme.


Code
====

    * Split the code handling on-disk storage from the interface code.

    * Refactor the save function to be less redundant.

    * Move the file handling code to GIO.


Other
=====

    * Provide a desktop file and possibly an icon.
